the more care you lavish on them,
the more they demand.

1118
01:29:11,353 --> 01:29:12,877
Rather like women.

1119
01:29:12,955 --> 01:29:14,616
I wouldn't know.

1120
01:29:14,690 --> 01:29:16,487
Take this verse in Saint Luke...

1121
01:29:16,559 --> 01:29:18,618
"It is the father's will
that nothing be lost."

1122
01:29:18,694 --> 01:29:21,754
In our language, the word "will"
denotes strength, willpower,

1123
01:29:21,831 --> 01:29:23,389
bending someone to your will.

1124
01:29:24,433 --> 01:29:28,028
But in the original Greek,
this three-letter word

1125
01:29:28,103 --> 01:29:31,129
denotes passion, fire,
inner organs.

1126
01:29:31,207 --> 01:29:35,371
It can mean beloved,
desire, even sexual desire.

1127
01:29:36,946 --> 01:29:38,311
Eat your porridge.

1128
01:29:38,380 --> 01:29:39,779
You're not even listening.

1129
01:29:39,849 --> 01:29:42,511
Besides, porridge does
nothing for my bowels.

1130
01:29:44,320 --> 01:29:47,949
No, it's not the word
that's important,

1131
01:29:48,023 --> 01:29:49,991
but what it's saying about God.

1132
