1144
01:30:42,011 --> 01:30:44,241
Just happened to be
in the wrong place,

1145
01:30:44,313 --> 01:30:47,646
got in the way of a mob of peasants
looting a monastery.

1146
01:30:47,716 --> 01:30:50,241
The whole world's
been turned upside-down

1147
