1223
01:38:34,750 --> 01:38:38,379
And... you still came here?

1224
01:38:38,453 --> 01:38:41,286
Because this is
where Dr. Luther lives.

1225
01:38:43,492 --> 01:38:47,087
Sir, we were smuggled out
in these herring barrels.

1226
01:38:47,162 --> 01:38:49,790
